data.description: LIVE by the WATER in this attractive 2700+sqft home in a waterfront community on Hilton Head. Preferred slab on grade design with ground-floor primary bedroom . Open floor-plan flows beautifully between large kitchen, living room, study, Carolina room & primary bedroom. Showcase kitchen offers stainless appliances, stone counters & custom cabinets. The fenced back yard (recently overhauled) offers privacy and is perfect for pets. Community deepwater dock available for boats/kayak and community pool. Skull Creek Bar/Restaurants close by.  Bring Your Golf Cart! ASSUMABLE LOW INTEREST LOAN approx 300k @ 3.75% Perfect place for boat enthusiasts
